public abstract class TestGraphicObject
extends DefaultTatamiTest

This abstract class permits to test some common method and properties of a GraphicObject. These tests even if they succeed don't guarented if the GraphicObject works correctly in a browser. But they are useful to assume some method and avoid some exception which can be thrown during the runtime.

Author:
Vianney
